  "plan": "## IlluminaExpressionFileCreator GenePattern Module — Implementation Plan\n\n### 1. Overview\nIlluminaExpressionFileCreator is a GenePattern module that Creates a GCT file from a zip of Illumina IDAT files and an Illumina manifest file\n\n### 2. Parameters\nThe module exposes 9 parameters:\n- Required: idat.zip, output.file\n- Optional: manifest, custom.manifest, background.subtraction.mode, collapse.mode, chip, custom.chip, clm\n\n### 3. Command Line\n```\n<java> <java_flags> -cp <libdir>IlluminaExpressionFileCreator.jar<path.separator><libdir>commons-cli-1.2.jar<path.separator><libdir>commons-codec-1.4.jar<path.separator><libdir>commons-io-1.4.jar<path.separator><libdir>commons-lang-2.5.jar<path.separator><libdir>dom4j-1.6.1.jar org.genepattern.illumina.expression.ExpressionFileCreator -manifestfile <custom.manifest> -manifesturl <manifest> -inputfile <idat.zip> -outputfile <output.file> -bg <background.subtraction.mode> -collapse <collapse.mode> -chipfile <custom.chip> -chipurl <chip> -clmfile <clm>\n```\n\n### 4. Docker Image\nDocker image: \n\n### 5. Validation Strategy\n- Validate all required parameters are provided\n- Validate file formats match expected extensions\n- Check parameter value ranges where applicable\n\n### 6. Implementation Roadmap\nPhase 1: Wrapper script implementation\nPhase 2: Docker container setup\nPhase 3: Parameter validation and error handling\nPhase 4: Testing and documentation",
  "wrapper_script": "IlluminaExpressionFileCreator.jar<path.separator><libdir>commons-cli-1.2.jar<path.separator><libdir>commons-codec-1.4.jar<path.separator><libdir>commons-io-1.4.jar<path.separator><libdir>commons-lang-2.5.jar<path.separator><libdir>dom4j-1.6.1.jar",
  "command_line": "<java> <java_flags> -cp <libdir>IlluminaExpressionFileCreator.jar<path.separator><libdir>commons-cli-1.2.jar<path.separator><libdir>commons-codec-1.4.jar<path.separator><libdir>commons-io-1.4.jar<path.separator><libdir>commons-lang-2.5.jar<path.separator><libdir>dom4j-1.6.1.jar org.genepattern.illumina.expression.ExpressionFileCreator -manifestfile <custom.manifest> -manifesturl <manifest> -inputfile <idat.zip> -outputfile <output.file> -bg <background.subtraction.mode> -collapse <collapse.mode> -chipfile <custom.chip> -chipurl <chip> -clmfile <clm>",
